org.baswell.httproxy
Class HttpResponse

java.lang.Object
  org.baswell.httproxy.HttpMessage
      org.baswell.httproxy.HttpResponse

public class HttpResponse
extends HttpMessage

A proxied HTTP response. The response sent back to the client can be modified in ProxyDirector.onResponseStart(HttpRequest, HttpResponse).
